entries.journal_entry_description: Take the lucrative job from Coris Mao in Mos Entha.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Coris Mao has an assignment for you. Talk to him  and find out about the job that he has for you.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Talk to Coris Mao in Mos Entha
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Go to the sand pirate base and scout the area.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Go to the Sand Pirate Base
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The pirates have stationed 2 guards outside the bunker. Kill them before you can get into the base.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: These pirates need to learn that they cannot terrorize innocents with impunity. Kill at least 10 of them.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: The pirate boss is holding these pirates together. Kill the boss to make sure that they don't reorganize.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: Great work! You put down the old dog and its pack. All that is left to do is to set the overload the reactor and get out. I don't know how long that reactor will last.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Sgt. Snopel sent you a message: Great work! You put down the old dog and its pack. All that is left to do is to set the overload the reactor and get out. I don't know how long that reactor will last.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Go to the main reactor and set it to overload. Then you must get out of the base.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Get out of the base before the reactor overloads!
entries.task09_comm_message_text: I'm actually impressed. You finished your mission with a minimum of mess. Head back to Coris Mao for your payment. I sent it to him already.
entries.task09_journal_entry_description: Sgt. Snopel sent you a final message: I'm actually impressed. You finished your mission with a minimum of mess. Head back to Coris Mao for your payment. I sent it to him already.
entries.task09_journal_entry_title: A Final Message from Sgt. Snopel
entries.task10_journal_entry_description: Coris Mao has your payment. Go talk to him to receive it.
entries.task10_journal_entry_title: Talk to Coris Mao in Mos Entha
